2. what should we give SID name in ASM ? 
=> whatever the name of database or whichever is run in 'ps -ef | grep pmon' that's called SID.

example ::

[grid@localhost ~]$ . oraenv
ORACLE_SID = [grid] ? +ASM
The Oracle base has been set to /u01/app/grid
